		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Translation project.
<br />
<br />LP's claim to fame is Konami's VRC7 mapper and heretofore intractable text. Most folks here, I think, are familiar with both the game and my <a href="http://agtp.romhack.net/" class="postlink">translation group.</a> I've got another thread further down the forum advertising translations for Madara and Esper Dream 2, both VRC6 games. (Although since AGTP got a redesign recently, the screenshot links are broken.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
