	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you want to save a little space in the ROM image. you can change the font graphics encoding to simple 1-bit packing instead of the bitplane RLE packing LP normally uses.
<br />
<br />At least, I think you can.  My memory isn't infallible!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


